OL,3,CSir Ed Davey blames 'Tory mess' for
OL,4,CLiberal Democrat council tax rises
OL,6,FSir Ed Davey was asked about council
OL,7,Ftax rises by ITV News Meridian's Kit
OL,8,FBradshaw in Eastbourne
OL,10,FSir Ed Davey has blamed Conservative
OL,11,Fmismanagement of local authorities and
OL,12,Fa lack of funding from central
OL,13,Fgovernment for council tax rises by
OL,14,Fthe Liberal Democrats.
OL,16,FThe party leader was responding to new
OL,17,Fanalysis which found that English
OL,18,Fcouncils run by the Lib Dems had
OL,19,Fimposed the highest average council
OL,20,Ftax rises for 2025/26.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
