OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774631480
OL,3,CSir Ed Davey blames 'Tory mess' for
OL,4,CLiberal Democrat council tax rises
OL,6,FSir Ed said his party was "clearing up
OL,7,Fthe mess of the Conservatives" who had
OL,8,Fleft several councils "basically
OL,9,Fbankrupt".
OL,11,F"Many councils are having to (increase
OL,12,Ftax), particularly where you've taken
OL,13,Fover from Conservatives who've tended
OL,14,Fto run councils very, very badly.
OL,16,F"Plus, without the support that really
OL,17,Fshould be coming from central
OL,18,Fgovernment ` particularly for things
OL,19,Flike special educational needs and
OL,20,Fadult social care ` councils across
OL,21,Fthe country are finding it tough."
