OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774631480
OL,3,CSir Ed Davey blames 'Tory mess' for
OL,4,CLiberal Democrat council tax rises
OL,6,FCouncils with either majority or
OL,7,Fminority Lib Dem control, imposed the
OL,8,Fhighest average core council tax
OL,9,Fincreases of 5.17%, according to the
OL,10,FPress Association.
OL,12,FBy contrast, their analysis found the
OL,13,Fmean average increase across the 13
OL,14,FReform-run councils was 4.15%, with
OL,15,Ffigures ranging from 1.99% in Durham
OL,16,Fto 8.98% in Worcestershire.
OL,18,FThe 78 councils controlled by Labour
OL,19,Fincreased bills by a mean average of
OL,20,F4.79% while the 26 Conservative
OL,21,Fcouncils pushed up bills by 4.92%.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
