OL,3,CSir Ed Davey blames 'Tory mess' for
OL,4,CLiberal Democrat council tax rises
OL,6,FThis Lib Dem figure reflects
OL,7,FGovernment-approved increases above
OL,8,Fthe normal 5% limit of 8.99% in
OL,9,FShropshire and 7.48% in Windsor &
OL,10,FMaidenhead.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
