OL,3,CSir Ed Davey blames 'Tory mess' for
OL,4,CLiberal Democrat council tax rises
OL,6,FAsked by ITV News Meridian why Lib
OL,7,FDems were increasing bills on average
OL,8,Fto a greater degree than other
OL,9,Fparties, Sir Ed said: "We want to make
OL,10,Fsure that those services are there for
OL,11,Fthe more vulnerable, for our children,
OL,12,Ffor our elderly people, and I just
OL,13,Fwish the government would sort out
OL,14,Fadult social care and special needs,
OL,15,Fso councils didn't have to put up
OL,16,Fcouncil tax."
OL,26,@qD@WOUxD@MO]
