OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774631480
OL,3,CSir Ed Davey blames 'Tory mess' for
OL,4,CLiberal Democrat council tax rises
OL,6,FThe Lib Dem leader cited Woking
OL,7,FBorough Council, in Surrey, and
OL,8,FWindsor and Maidenhead Borough
OL,9,FCouncil, in Berkshire ` both
OL,10,Fpreviously run by the Conservatives `
OL,11,Fas examples of where relatively new
OL,12,FLib Dem administrations have had to
OL,13,Fincrease taxes.
OL,15,FSir Ed Davey was speaking on a visit
OL,16,Fto a parent and baby group in
OL,17,FEastbourne, East Sussex, ahead of
OL,18,Flocal elections across large parts of
OL,19,Fthe South East on 7 May.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
