OL,3,CSir Ed Davey blames 'Tory mess' for
OL,4,CLiberal Democrat council tax rises
OL,6,FThe interview follows Reform UK's
OL,7,FNigel Farage and the Conservative
OL,8,Fleader Kemi Badenoch both defending
OL,9,Ftheir councillors for increasing
OL,10,Fcouncil tax, despite separate promises
OL,11,Fat last year's local elections to
OL,12,Flower bills.
OL,14,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,15,Four political experts are across all
OL,16,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,17,Fto the latest episode below...
